{"tid":1753614,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"15歲中學生因攜帶雷射筆，被裁定管有攻擊性武器罪成，被判入更生中心。","createTime":"2019-11-25T03:36:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-28T03:19:08.000Z","uid":61672,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ce65c1cb317e901924d33eb5a03a8f0ce821d82f","tid":1753614,"uid":61672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T03:36:27.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】一名15歲中學生因攜帶雷射筆，被裁定管有攻擊性武器罪成，被判入更生中心。<br />\n<br />\n涉案學生9月21日，在屯門站附被發現攜有一枝雷射筆及經改裝的長傘及行山杖等。辯方求情指，被告被捕後還柙至今，希望判處可即時獲釋的刑期，以繼續學業，但裁判官認為更生中心提供有系統訓練，相信有助被告改過自身，加強守法意識，又指年輕人可以有自己意見，但必須以合法方式表達，於示威或集會中持有攻擊性武器，可威脅前線執法人員安全及社會秩序，亦妨礙其他人和平表達訴求的權利。裁判官拒絕辯方保釋，等候上訴申請。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=371139&amp;refer=\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D371139%26refer%3D&d=dTdn096UhK%2BcydR5vLM294kJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=d5563ac5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D371139%26refer%3D&h=526c0acf\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=371139&amp;refer=</a><br />\n<br />\n香港法治已死<br />\n區選已完<br />\n義士一個個被清算中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e30219f85edf23112a6142ea30a51068560eb58","tid":1753614,"uid":279650,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T03:53:02.000Z","msg":"dklm"},{"pid":"70537047efd5bb1258cb2edab8891c82a8cffafb","tid":1753614,"uid":304321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T03:55:04.000Z","msg":"一定要上訴啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2edfd3e1c964dfae1961b12bddf49a0447989b1a","tid":1753614,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T03: